Enable the spice remote desktop protocol. Valid options are
.RS 4
.IP "\fBport=<nr>\fR" 4
.IX Item "port=<nr>"
Set the \s-1TCP\s0 port spice is listening on for plaintext channels.
.IP "\fBaddr=<addr>\fR" 4
